    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、お疲れ様……って、うわ\nここにあるの、全部結婚情報誌か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ good work… Wait‚ huh?\nAre all these magazines here about weddings?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……\n結婚って……なんなんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san…\nWhat is… marriage‚ I wonder?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり哲学みたいな質問だな……\n月ストのみんなが心配してたぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's quite a philosophical question out of the blue…\nEveryone in Moon Tempest was worried‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そうですよね、すみません\nでも、調べれば調べるほど分からなくなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… That's right‚ I'm sorry.\nBut the more I research‚ the less I understand…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "例えばこの雑誌なんですけど\n結婚した人100人にアンケートを取っているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ this magazine here…\nThey're conducting surveys with 100 married people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "結婚して本当に楽しいって人もいれば\n結婚しない方が良かったなんて人もいて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Some say they're truly happy after getting married‚\nwhile others say they wish they hadn't gotten married.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "結婚って誰もが幸せになるものじゃないんでしょうか\nだんだん分からなくなってきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't marriage supposed to make everyone happy?\nI'm starting to lose sight of it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
