      "text": "あまり考え過ぎは良くないぞ……と言いたいが\nそうもいかないよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not good to overthink it too much… Although I want to say that.\nBut it's not that simple‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
