      "text": "『結婚式を検討中の人』『結婚に憧れる人』\n向けの写真ですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These are photos for those who are\n\"considering a wedding\" or \"dreaming of marriage.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
