      "text": "結婚情報誌を寮でもずっと読んでたら\n優と莉央さんが通り掛かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While I was reading wedding magazines in the dorm‚\nYu and Rio-san happened to pass by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも目を丸くしてて……優に\n「琴乃ちゃん、結婚でもするん？」って聞かれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of them had surprised expressions… Yu asked me‚\n\"Kotono-chan‚ are you planning to get married?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
